The,Fleet,Genius,REST,API,provides,developers,access,to,the,functionality,and,vehicle,data,of,Fleet,Genius,for,integration,with,other,applications,The,API,can,be,used,for,fleet,management,but,can,also,be,used,in,asset,management,and,accounting,fuel,use,monitoring,and,emissions,testing,The,API,provides,information,on,vehicle,speed,RPM,trips,durations,distance,driven,fuel,burned,GPS,location,check,engine,status,lights,and,diagnostic,trouble,codes,Fleet,Genius,is,a,fleet,management,platform